<section id="contact" class="page-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="heading-container">
            <h2 class="heading-main">Contacto</h2>
            <p class="heading-sub">
                ¿Tienes alguna pregunta o quieres trabajar juntos? Completa el
                formulario y me pondré en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-container">
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mblzlndn" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Nombre</label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="name"
                        name="name"
                        class="form-input"
                        required
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        id="email"
                        name="email"
                        class="form-input"
                        required
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message" class="form-label">Mensaje</label>
                    <textarea
                        id="message"
                        name="message"
                        rows="5"
                        class="form-input"
                        required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Enviar Mensaje</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .page-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 1100px;
        width: 90%;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* --- Títulos --- */
    .heading-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .heading-main {
        font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .heading-sub {
        font-size: var(--font-size-md);
        color: var(--color-texto-secundario);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* --- Formulario --- */
    .form-container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: var(--color-fondo-secundario);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .form-label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
        color: var(--color-texto-secundario);
    }
    .form-input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: var(--font-size-md);
        font-family: inherit;
        background-color: var(--color-fondo);
        color: var(--color-texto-principal);
    }
    .form-input:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: var(--color-primario);
    }

    /* --- Botón --- */
    .btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        background: var(--color-texto-principal);
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: var(--font-size-md);
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
</style>
